{"tid":1893301,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"抗疫期間會去西貢嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-02-23T07:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T09:59:02.000Z","uid":278846,"like":43,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"466cfdde9229ef7cd6b891b4855b06db306ace8f","tid":1893301,"uid":278846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"首先，我屌哂你班自私撚先。<br />\n你班死港豬，以為西貢好撚安全，錯撚哂喇！仲幻想西貢行街唔會中招，成個西貢仲旺過旺角呀，架架巴士小巴坐滿人，私家車又係咁車入嚟，撞車嗰陣條公路都冇咁塞，入到嚟又要唔戴罩，岩岩落街買餸都嚇撚死。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8MQXZMe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8MQXZMe.jpg&h=4bd36983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最重要係，西貢有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3個隔離營</span></strong>架！</span>以為行街實冇死？唔好意思，個營喺你隔離祝你好運。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6q1Tx58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6q1Tx58.jpg&h=f133c22f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該你執返自己啲口罩個垃圾，咪撚周圍掉。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人，咪咁自私啦，想出街又唔驚自己社區爆發就去人哋社區，西貢人唔撚係人？見到你哋一車車入嚟集體傳染，都唔知你哋係冇腦定on9。<br />\n<br />\n今日帶遊行架，咁撚得閒行咩山，去遊行啦屌。"},{"pid":"70a3e2ab43c054a28a5bca744a542cb2cc114233","tid":1893301,"uid":278846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"最尾 有遊行，打得快打錯"},{"pid":"c09ed27938ceee0777bd5734d1d3a35f614f2a72","tid":1893301,"uid":278846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:11:38.000Z","msg":"屌你班港豬"},{"pid":"e60de44bc5e79e412ab65708a7d7efe92926095c","tid":1893301,"uid":1632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:13:15.000Z","msg":"真 啱啱見入西灣亭架車排哂隊"},{"pid":"75990dff7d8253e93e73890a4e9a7735aa1f7b18","tid":1893301,"uid":278846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e60de44bc5e79e412ab65708a7d7efe92926095c","tid":1893301,"uid":1632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTim